                                </entry>
                                <entry align="center"></entry>
                                <entry align="center">
                                    <para>X</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>
                                    <para>3. Not used on Internationals- Do not change.</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry align="center"></entry>
                                <entry align="center">
                                    <para>X</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>
                                    <para>4. Drivers door automatically unlocks when ignition is turned off or Parking
                                        Brake is applied.
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry align="center">
                                    <para>X</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry align="center"></entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>
                                    <para>5. Not used on Internationals- Do not change.</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry align="center"></entry>
                                <entry align="center">
                                    <para>X</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>
                                    <para>6. Illuminated exit when Parking Brake is applied or ignition is turned off.
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
